cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

The paper discusses the application of deep and recurrent neural networks to a control task, specifically locomotion. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). Among these, machine learning and robotics are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the topic of the paper. Artificial intelligence and neural and evolutionary computing are also likely as they are closely related to machine learning. Systems and control is less likely as it is a broader category that encompasses various control-related topics.
